    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金因关注美联储降息路径和股市暴跌而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gold-closes-in-on-record-after-weak-july-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价下跌，扭转了早前的涨势，因为人们对美联储降息步伐过慢的担忧日益加剧，导致股市疲软，令金价承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gold-closes-in-on-record-after-weak-july-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 12:44:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市遭遇一年多来最差单日跌幅 抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/european-stocks-extend-drop-amid-global-selloff-before-us-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告弱于预期，引发人们对经济增长的担忧，并加剧了科技股的暴跌，欧洲股市延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/european-stocks-extend-drop-amid-global-selloff-before-us-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
